        <h2>Networking Expert — Enterprise Networks &amp; Protocol Architecture</h2>

        <div class="two-col-text-img">
          <div>
            <p>Dr. Lavian is a networking expert and <a href="/">telecommunications expert witness</a> who provides consulting services in <a href="/communications-expert-witness/network-communications-expert-witness/">network communications</a>, telecommunications, and <a href="/communications-expert-witness/internet-expert-witness/">internet</a> protocols. He also serves as an <a href="/communications-expert-witness/internet-expert-witness/">internet expert witness</a>. He profoundly understands network <a href="/us-10348313-radar-target-detection-system/">communications</a>, data communications, computer networks, and internet protocols, including TCP/IP, UDP, IP, MAC Ethernet, and IEEE 802.3.</p>

            <p>With his academic background and practical industry experience, Dr. Lavian comprehensively understands the relationships between <a href="/us-20130080898-electronic-communications/">network communications</a>, computer networks, data communications, and <a href="/us-20180130102-reliable-rating-system-and-method-thereof/">wireless</a> applications. He is highly skilled in designing, implementing, and architecture communications services in these fields. Dr. Lavian's expertise makes him a valuable resource for clients seeking expert consulting services in network communications.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
